bonc-0.1.5   2008-10-01 15:45

 * Fixed a small problem with escaping characters for HTML generation.
 * Fixed null pointer bug when printing html output for input with no system.
 * Fixed bug in auto-generating class dictionaries where a class description is omitted.
 * Fixed null pointer exception thrown when reporting errors involving input from stdin.
 * Now using class descriptions from the cluster chart(s) if none is given in the class chart.
 * Improved some error messages and source location reporting of errors.
 * Added ability to display clustering graphs via the -g icg option, using the prefuse library.
 * Added emacs bon-mode (Debian).
 * Added basic gedit highlighting, and mime-type text/x-bon for .bon files (Debian).


bonc-0.1.4   2008-03-24 13:01

 * Fixed bug that caused incorrect line-numbers to be reported for certain inputs.
 * Added initial version of bash auto-complete script for debian build (should also work for other bash systems).


bonc-0.1.3   2008-03-06 20:47

 * Added support for HTML printing of informal charts (see the usage section of the README.txt).
 * Class charts can now be generated as a printing option, or automatically as part of normal printing.
 * Now allowing explanation, indexing and part terms inside of class dictionaries.


bonc-0.1.2   2008-02-26 16:06

 * Now allowing parenthesized cluster names in involves and creates clauses.


bonc-0.1.1   2008-02-26 16:01

 * Initial release.



